    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p><b>IndiaOffers.in</b> is a deals-and-savings platform built for one simple mission: <b>nobody in India should ever overpay while shopping online.</b> Every day our team scans Amazon, Flipkart, Myntra, Ajio and dozens of other stores for the kind of prices that make you look twice — <b>loot deals at 80–90% off, ₹1 deals, free products, price-error steals and coupon stacks</b> that most shoppers never find on their own.</p>
