      <li><b>Buying guides that tell the truth.</b> Best AC, best TV, best phone — with honest pros and cons, so you buy right the first time.</li>
      <li><b>Alerts that work for you.</b> Tell us which bank cards you hold and which categories you love — we ping you the moment a sale drops on them.</li>
